This was a matter that appeared capable of proof or disproof and

the observations necessary are now being made. As yet they are few

in number, but, so far as they go, significant. Thus -

Ancon village, a former hotbed of malaria, produces only A. apicimaculata;

Pedro Miguel River, 800 yards from houses, produces only A. apicimaculata;

Swamp 7, Cristobal, 800 yards from houses, produces only A. apicimaculata;

Swamp 4, Cristobal, 800 yards from houses, frequented only by cattle,

produces only A. apicimaculata.

